00:01:42.270 --> 00:01:45.290
of like have kind of an open free form conversation about what

00:01:45.290 --> 00:01:46.620
we've seen has worked.

00:01:46.620 --> 00:01:48.900
Clearly, there's a lot of things that are not working

00:01:49.150 --> 00:01:49.800
with media.

