Do we have any SIL users in the house?

00:05:17.000 --> 00:05:17.960
Fantastic.

00:05:17.960 --> 00:05:21.730
And I won't even mention what SIL kind of resembles

00:05:21.730 --> 00:05:23.960
from previous iterations of this.

00:05:23.960 --> 00:05:27.080
But SIL is just a fantastic news aggregation app.

00:05:27.080 --> 00:05:30.820
And so you log in with your blue sky account, with

00:05:30.820 --> 00:05:35.210
your atmosphere account, with your Mastodon account even

00:05:35.330 --> 00:05:35.510
.

00:05:35.560 --> 00:05:38.460
