00:05:48.070 --> 00:05:51.220
little bit about kind of your experience building SIL and,

00:05:51.220 --> 00:05:54.520
and some of the conversations that you've had with publishers and

00:05:54.540 --> 00:05:56.030
what resonates with them.

00:05:56.040 --> 00:05:56.520
Yeah.

00:05:56.520 --> 00:05:57.800
Yeah.

00:05:58.160 --> 00:05:58.440
Yeah.

00:05:58.440 --> 00:06:01.280
So I'm mostly known in the AT Pro space for S

00:06:01.340 --> 00:06:01.480
IL.

00:06:01.480 --> 00:06:06.070
Most of how I pay my bills is through consulting for news

00:06:06.970 --> 00:06:07.320
organizations.

