Okay.

00:07:20.730 --> 00:07:21.500
Small amount.

00:07:21.500 --> 00:07:24.120
How many people are more like builders in this space?

00:07:24.120 --> 00:07:25.460
Okay.

00:07:25.590 --> 00:07:26.620
Almost everybody.

00:07:26.620 --> 00:07:27.110
Great.

00:07:27.110 --> 00:07:28.820
Um, so I feel like I can come with this from

00:07:28.930 --> 00:07:30.440
two perspectives, right?

00:07:30.440 --> 00:07:33.650
Why news organizations should be buying on AT pro buying in on

00:07:33.650 --> 00:07:35.510
AT proto and also why they're not yet.

00:07:35.510 --> 00:07:37.720
I think I can sort of give both sides of this.

