So I think I'm going to tailor what I say to

00:07:39.770 --> 00:07:41.040
why they're not yet.

00:07:41.040 --> 00:07:43.160
Um, given who we have in the room.

00:07:43.160 --> 00:07:47.010
Um, so I think, you know, having them join

00:07:47.010 --> 00:07:50.690
blue sky is great and like, uh, you know,

00:07:50.690 --> 00:07:55.520
blue sky offers, uh, better traffic and referral traffic than

00:07:55.520 --> 00:07:57.980
the other platforms because it doesn't downrank links.

00:07:57.980 --> 00:08:00.240
It has tools like SIL in the ecosystem that even do

