And I'm wondering if you have seen anything that has really

00:11:48.150 --> 00:11:51.500
moved the needle, like in the feeds that you've created

00:11:51.500 --> 00:11:54.930
, um, are, are there opportunities to either give news

00:11:54.930 --> 00:11:58.600
organizations more feedback or allow them to kind of have some more

00:11:58.600 --> 00:12:00.040
control over some of those things?

00:12:00.040 --> 00:12:06.760
Um, so like more control over like what specific things?

00:12:06.760 --> 00:12:09.700
Um, well, you know, so the content that they

00:12:09.700 --> 00:12:12.010
're putting out, um, whether that's on their own

